[SPEAKER_00] s ton idejom

568
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:54,279
[SPEAKER_00] da treba biti

569
00:20:54,279 --> 00:20:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] što više stranaca

570
00:21:01,359 --> 00:21:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] istraživanje

571
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] onog najpoznatijih

572
00:21:02,599 --> 00:21:03,519
[SPEAKER_00] svjetskih politologa

573
00:21:03,519 --> 00:21:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] Roberta Patnama

574
00:21:04,359 --> 00:21:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] kojom je radio tamo

575
00:21:05,059 --> 00:21:06,200
[SPEAKER_00] negdje sredinom 90-ih,

576
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:07,259
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je zapravo

577
00:21:07,259 --> 00:21:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] pronašao u Americi

578
00:21:08,099 --> 00:21:08,940
[SPEAKER_00] što je zajednica

579
00:21:08,940 --> 00:21:10,819
[SPEAKER_00] rasno kulturna raznolikija,

580
00:21:10,819 --> 00:21:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] to je manje

581
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:12,799
[SPEAKER_00] socijalno povjerenje,

582
00:21:12,799 --> 00:21:14,359
[SPEAKER_00] to je manje solidarnosti

583
00:21:14,359 --> 00:21:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] među ljudima,

584
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:16,059
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo kohezije

585
00:21:16,059 --> 00:21:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] manje u društvu.

586
00:21:17,119 --> 00:21:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znači i nepovjerenje

587
00:21:18,420 --> 00:21:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne pada samo

588
00:21:19,019 --> 00:21:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] između pripadnika

589
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:20,819
[SPEAKER_00] različitih zajednica,

590
00:21:20,819 --> 00:21:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] nego i općento

591
00:21:21,420 --> 00:21:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] između iste zajednice

592
00:21:22,380 --> 00:21:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno povjerenje.

593
00:21:24,059 --> 00:21:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je veza,

594
00:21:25,079 --> 00:21:25,759
[SPEAKER_01] to je potpuno,

595
00:21:25,759 --> 00:21:27,480
[SPEAKER_01] ovo što je Patnama postavio,

596
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,740
[SPEAKER_01] je potpuno logično.

597
00:21:29,740 --> 00:21:31,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ti s čovjekom

598
00:21:31,460 --> 00:21:32,220
[SPEAKER_01] kojim si ti,

599
00:21:32,220 --> 00:21:33,279
[SPEAKER_01] cilje kohezije,

600
00:21:33,279 --> 00:21:34,160
[SPEAKER_01] jedinstvo je cilj,

601
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,579
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno da mi što bolje

602
00:21:35,579 --> 00:21:36,420
[SPEAKER_01] jedni drugi razumijemo.

603
00:21:36,420 --> 00:21:36,700
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, da.

604
00:21:36,700 --> 00:21:38,440
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, ako ja čovjeka

605
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] koji gledam preko puta sebe,

606
00:21:40,079 --> 00:21:41,579
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam neki dan sjedela u tramvu

607
00:21:41,579 --> 00:21:43,240
[SPEAKER_01] i gledam jedan simpatičan

608
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:45,059
[SPEAKER_01] mladi čovjek stranac

609
00:21:45,059 --> 00:21:46,059
[SPEAKER_01] koji ovdje očito radi,

610
00:21:46,059 --> 00:21:47,220
[SPEAKER_01] ja sad njega gledam,

611
00:21:47,220 --> 00:21:48,440
[SPEAKER_01] ja se mislim da na njegovom mjestu

612
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:50,720
[SPEAKER_01] sjedi jedan dečko iz Zagreba.

613
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ja za njega,

614
00:21:51,779 --> 00:21:53,420
[SPEAKER_01] na pet osnovnih pitanjima

615
00:21:53,420 --> 00:21:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] o tome gdje,

616
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:55,220
[SPEAKER_01] što on misli o nečemu,

617
00:21:55,220 --> 00:21:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] bi znala dati

618
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:57,579
[SPEAKER_01] dosta dobru procenu.

619
00:21:57,579 --> 00:21:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ja za ovog čovjeka

620
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:00,059
[SPEAKER_01] uopće ništa ne znam.

621
00:22:00,059 --> 00:22:02,200
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam kako on reagira

622
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,160
[SPEAKER_01] na određene stvari,

623
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,579
[SPEAKER_01] koja je vjerojatnost

624
00:22:04,579 --> 00:22:05,980
[SPEAKER_01] da će reagirat na određen način.

625
00:22:05,980 --> 00:22:06,240
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

626
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] to je jednostavno nepoznavanje

627
00:22:08,099 --> 00:22:09,279
[SPEAKER_01] uz puno poštovanje

628
00:22:09,279 --> 00:22:10,559
[SPEAKER_01] njegovog dostojanstva

629
00:22:10,559 --> 00:22:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] i tko je on.

630
00:22:11,460 --> 00:22:12,740
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, to je ko kad mi odemo

631
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:14,660
[SPEAKER_01] u Nepal u konačnicu.

632
00:22:14,759 --> 00:22:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] I sva istraživanja

633
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] ipak pokazuju

634
00:22:16,559 --> 00:22:17,640
[SPEAKER_00] da su ljudi prvenstveno

635
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] usmjereni najviše

636
00:22:19,119 --> 00:22:20,140
[SPEAKER_00] ipak na svoju zajednicu.

637
00:22:20,140 --> 00:22:21,779
[SPEAKER_00] Znači nije to samo u Hrvatsku,

638
00:22:21,779 --> 00:22:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] tako i u Nizemsku.

639
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je među onih

640
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:24,819
[SPEAKER_00] najkozmopolitskim nacijama,

641
00:22:24,819 --> 00:22:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] koje je.

642
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] One su usmjerene

643
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:27,799
[SPEAKER_00] i prema svijetu,

644
00:22:27,799 --> 00:22:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] stalo in je do svijeta,

645
00:22:29,059 --> 00:22:29,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali su nekako ipak

646
00:22:29,859 --> 00:22:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] i dalje dominantno usmjerene

647
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] na svoju zajednicu.

648
00:22:32,380 --> 00:22:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] Upućene su na svoje ljude i ljudi.

649
00:22:33,900 --> 00:22:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali naravno kažen,

650
00:22:35,119 --> 00:22:36,339
[SPEAKER_00] ipak su tu jake snage,

651
00:22:36,339 --> 00:22:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] to treba reći,

652
00:22:37,579 --> 00:22:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] ipak su tu jake, jake snage,

653
00:22:39,039 --> 00:22:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] globalne i prvenstveno ekonomske,

654
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:43,200
[SPEAKER_00] koje je zapravo na neki način

655
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] žele ukidanje svih mogućih granica

656
00:22:45,019 --> 00:22:46,740
[SPEAKER_00] i da se mi zapravo pretvorimo

657
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:47,359
[SPEAKER_00] u neku vrstu,

658
00:22:47,359 --> 00:22:47,859
[SPEAKER_00] ja bih rekao,

659
00:22:47,859 --> 00:22:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] permisivnog potrošaškog pojedinca.

660
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:53,079
[SPEAKER_00] Da se lišimo svi ti nekih identiteta

661
00:22:53,079 --> 00:22:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] pripadnosti zajednici,

662
00:22:54,420 --> 00:22:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] osim određenih identiteta,

663
00:22:56,119 --> 00:22:56,839
[SPEAKER_00] ti mogu obstat,

664
00:22:56,839 --> 00:22:58,819
[SPEAKER_00] ali zapravo nacionalnog identiteta,

665
00:22:58,819 --> 00:22:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] zavičaja i tako dalje,

666
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,700
[SPEAKER_00] ideja je,

667
00:23:00,700 --> 00:23:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] jer onda zapravo taj globalni kapital

668
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:04,799
[SPEAKER_00] može lako,

669
00:23:04,799 --> 00:23:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] ako vi nate identiteta,

670
00:23:07,319 --> 00:23:08,319
[SPEAKER_00] vi onda ne želite možda

671
00:23:08,319 --> 00:23:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] kupiti neki proizvod vaše zemlje,

672
00:23:10,599 --> 00:23:12,700
[SPEAKER_00] otići u neko vaše turičiško odredište,

673
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] nego je ideja.

674
00:23:13,980 --> 00:23:16,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ne želite jačati svog čovjeka

675
00:23:16,819 --> 00:23:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] koji proizvodi nešto u Hrvatskoj,

676
00:23:18,380 --> 00:23:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] nema te osjeće odgovornosti za njega.

677
00:23:20,519 --> 00:23:21,559
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ste potrošač,

678
00:23:21,559 --> 00:23:23,119
[SPEAKER_01] vi niste više pripadnik neke zajednice,

679
00:23:23,119 --> 00:23:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] nego s tobrišan potrošač.

680
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:24,980
[SPEAKER_01] Samo to, tako je,

681
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:25,920
[SPEAKER_01] to je glavna karakteristika.

682
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:26,220
[SPEAKER_01] Da, to je to.

683
00:23:26,220 --> 00:23:27,740
[SPEAKER_01] I u principu to predstavlja,

684
00:23:27,740 --> 00:23:30,680
[SPEAKER_01] u sve drugo predstavlja jedno osiromašenje.

685
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] Da će se oduzima ta tvoja boja,

686
00:23:33,059 --> 00:23:33,900
[SPEAKER_01] tvoj kolorit.

687
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da će rast nejednakosti,

688
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] jer uvijek će biti neki jači

689
00:23:36,559 --> 00:23:37,660
[SPEAKER_00] koji će dominirati.

690
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:38,140
[SPEAKER_00] To je to.

691
00:23:38,140 --> 00:23:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, mi zapravo imamo tu ideju

692
00:23:40,380 --> 00:23:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] iz ostanka brige i odgovornosti

693
00:23:42,940 --> 00:23:43,660
[SPEAKER_00] za zajednicu.

694
00:23:43,660 --> 00:23:45,359
[SPEAKER_00] I nažalost, ono što se nama nameće

695
00:23:45,359 --> 00:23:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] je da je to sve nazadno,

696
00:23:47,980 --> 00:23:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] da je to sve fašističko,

697
00:23:49,619 --> 00:23:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] rasističko i tako dalje.

698
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:53,259
[SPEAKER_00] da je to diskriminatorno,

699
00:23:53,259 --> 00:23:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] ako na nje stalo do naše nacionalne zajednice,

700
00:23:56,119 --> 00:23:57,440
[SPEAKER_00] što je sasvim legitimno i prirodno.

701
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, i vrijedi u svim državama.

702
00:23:59,380 --> 00:24:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] Svi se brinu, gdje se brinu,

703
00:24:01,519 --> 00:24:02,720
[SPEAKER_01] gdje imaju tri čiste se brinu,

704
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:03,779
[SPEAKER_01] se brinu o svojoj nacionalni.

705
00:24:03,779 --> 00:24:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je uvijek fora, moram reći,

706
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:07,980
[SPEAKER_01] kad čitam neke od kolumnista,

707
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] mainstream media,

708
00:24:08,619 --> 00:24:10,920
[SPEAKER_01] koji su u komunizmu isto tako imali,

709
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:14,079
[SPEAKER_01] bili dio tog sustava,

710
00:24:14,079 --> 00:24:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] koji je držao, dakle,

711
00:24:15,619 --> 00:24:17,259
[SPEAKER_01] potpuno zatvorene granice,

712
00:24:17,259 --> 00:24:19,839
[SPEAKER_01] a sada oni mudruju o tome

713
00:24:19,839 --> 00:24:22,319
[SPEAKER_01] kako se svi mi trebamo otvoriti.

714
00:24:22,319 --> 00:24:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, kod tih ljudi je slučaj zapravo

715
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] da je njima ta Hrvatska uvijek nekako

716
00:24:26,119 --> 00:24:27,779
[SPEAKER_00] pretjesna, premračna.

717
00:24:27,779 --> 00:24:29,680
[SPEAKER_00] Napravo, njima je ta cijela ideja Hrvatske,

718
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi rekao,

719
00:24:31,299 --> 00:24:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] da neki način Hrvatske,

720
00:24:33,619 --> 00:24:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] u koji ipak većinu čine Hrvati,

721
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvati imaju vlast i tako dalje,

722
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:39,400
[SPEAKER_00] to je njima preodbojno.

723
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:41,319
[SPEAKER_00] Tu oni vide odmah nešto mračno,

724
00:24:41,319 --> 00:24:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] fašističko i tako dalje.

725
00:24:43,099 --> 00:24:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] I zato je to njima,

726
00:24:45,019 --> 00:24:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] zato je ta priča ista.

727
00:24:47,259 --> 00:24:48,339
[SPEAKER_00] jer uvijek je zapravo problem,

728
00:24:48,339 --> 00:24:49,700
[SPEAKER_00] ako je to Hrvatska,

729
00:24:49,700 --> 00:24:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] koja je naravno liberalno-demokratska država,

730
00:24:52,500 --> 00:24:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj svi građani imaju jednaka prava,

731
00:24:54,539 --> 00:24:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali opet, ako je tu ipak Hrvati većina

732
00:24:56,940 --> 00:24:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] i Hrvati imaju vlast,

733
00:24:57,980 --> 00:24:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] to je onda problem.

734
00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:01,319
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nije mlako.

735
00:25:01,319 --> 00:25:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] Vezano za, dakle, rješenja

736
00:25:06,500 --> 00:25:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] i vezano za diasporno, za Hrvatske,

737
00:25:09,420 --> 00:25:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] ti se time i bavio dosta.

738
00:25:11,359 --> 00:25:14,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kako sad ti tu vidiš koje su realne opcije,

739
00:25:14,519 --> 00:25:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] evo, u nekakvom ovim silnicama

740
00:25:17,559 --> 00:25:18,779
[SPEAKER_01] za Hrvatsku,

741
00:25:18,779 --> 00:25:21,480
[SPEAKER_01] vezano za te ljude koje mi imamo izvan države?

742
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, tu je naravno velike su tu razlike,

743
00:25:23,980 --> 00:25:25,220
[SPEAKER_00] jer vi sad imate, ne znam,

744
00:25:25,220 --> 00:25:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] nekim držama, poput Sjednje međučkih država,

745
00:25:27,279 --> 00:25:28,319
[SPEAKER_00] ili Čile, Argentine,

746
00:25:28,319 --> 00:25:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] vi sad već imate petu, šestu generaciju

747
00:25:30,460 --> 00:25:32,779
[SPEAKER_00] iseljenika, potomaka,

748
00:25:32,779 --> 00:25:33,660
[SPEAKER_00] iseljenika.

749
00:25:34,359 --> 00:25:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Negdje drugdje imate možda drugu, treću generaciju,

750
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je sad Njemačka ili Austrija,

751
00:25:39,079 --> 00:25:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] koja je naravno i bliže.

752
00:25:41,019 --> 00:25:42,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja među da će svima njima i dalje

753
00:25:42,559 --> 00:25:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatska ostati onako dosta bliska.

754
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:48,059
[SPEAKER_00] Oni imaju ipak neki identitet.

755
00:25:48,059 --> 00:25:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, onima kojima je fizički,

756
00:25:50,380 --> 00:25:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] teritorijalno bliža,

757
00:25:51,900 --> 00:25:54,500
[SPEAKER_00] bit će više upućeni na Hrvatsku.

758
00:25:54,500 --> 00:25:55,740
[SPEAKER_00] A onda, s druge strane,

759
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] tu je onda situacija Hrvata u Bosni i Hrvatske

760
00:25:58,519 --> 00:25:59,339
[SPEAKER_00] koje nisu diaspora,

761
00:25:59,339 --> 00:26:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] one su tamo autohtoni narod.

762
00:26:00,539 --> 00:26:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] I pitanje je, šta će se tu dogoditi?

763
00:26:02,500 --> 00:26:04,339
[SPEAKER_00] Da li će zapravo svi Hrvati iz BiH

764
00:26:04,339 --> 00:26:05,180
[SPEAKER_00] završiti u Hrvatskoj?

765
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:08,640
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, to ne bi bilo dobro za Hrvate u BiH,

766
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:10,339
[SPEAKER_00] ali to se čine neki procesi

767
00:26:10,339 --> 00:26:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] koji su očito neumetni.

768
00:26:12,019 --> 00:26:13,339
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan veliki,

769
00:26:13,339 --> 00:26:14,779
[SPEAKER_00] da ćemo mi zapravo tražiti

770
00:26:14,779 --> 00:26:17,140
[SPEAKER_00] stalno to nekako osnaživanje demografsko

